sub_title: sociologe - helping expat women to thrive in the Netherlands
summary:
During my studies at the University Leiden I specialized in Gender, Globalisation and Social Policy and the Position of Women in the Middle East. This has made me aware of the special position  and emancipation of women in the world. 

I am interested in Greek mythology, in live. The 7 Goddesses within every woman âœ¨

I have loved to organize Greek Goddesses Workshops for Expatwomen over the years. I hope to guide women and to re-discover new paths in live (Ken je Klassieke Godin ðŸ˜‰)

As a workshoptrainer I work with intuition, visualizations, personal awareness and personal growth to re-discover hidden Archetypes within yourself in order to change their inner landscape. I hope to inspire the local community women in Eindhoven to see what we can recognize and learn from each other. In order to inspire and discover new paths ðŸ¤  in live.

In these workshops several subjects I have guided women in..
* Personal Growth and Career development
* Conscious Awareness - Mindfulness
* How can I use slow movement - Hestia (insight)
* The Art of Networking: Wild Artemis
* Nothing is what it seems (Persephone)
* Athena Goddess of the (hand) work - Better Wise than smart
* Demeter Goddess. How care is of utmost importance and how to raise kids
* Hera - What can I learn from my partner?
* Aphrodita - What is beauty to you? How does/has she influenced your life
